A-2 â€” Scientific gloss (English + short VN paraphrase) â€” put these in the personalization or keep as appendix
1.	Predictive processing â€” brain constantly predicts input and updates on surprise.
VN: nÃ£o dá»± Ä‘oÃ¡n vÃ  há»c tá»« â€œbáº¥t ngá»â€.
