5.	Meta-monitoring â€” monitoring oneâ€™s own cognition; â€œthinking about thinkingâ€.
VN: tá»± giÃ¡m sÃ¡t tÆ° duy.
6.	Default Mode Network (DMN) â€” brain network active in mind-wandering / imagery.
