7.	Reward-prediction error â€” dopaminergic signal for surprising reward â†’ learning.
VN: â€œnÃ£o khenâ€ khi dá»± Ä‘oÃ¡n bá»‹ sá»­a â†’ lÆ°u há»c.
8.	Task-switching cost â€” performance penalty when switching tasks (math â†’ vÄƒn).
